{
    "description_long": "This is a double grave plot bordered by a low, rectangular fence made of black stone or polished granite, set on a reddish-brown tiled base. At the head of the plot are two upright headstones, each with engraved portraits, names, and dates, separated by a central reddish-brown stone panel. A white angel statue sits atop the central panel, adding a decorative and solemn touch. The headstones feature Cyrillic inscriptions and a prominent cross engraved between them. The grave is designed with a clean, geometric layout, and the tiled surface is divided into square sections. The overall appearance is formal and respectful, suitable for a cemetery or memorial park.",
